\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"94ff5924-283a-4bf6-9935-ed739a6a4a3c"],

Cell["Answer To D: Collapse Of Broad Unreduced Differences", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"bc55452e-bc8c-4251-b5c7-7350ce700ca2"],

Cell["\<\
Yes, at exact current-family level and with the corrected reduced semantics.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"09679d91-4de5-4cb1-849e-76e3fe700a07"],

Cell["\<\
The exact lane supports the statement that broad unreduced seam differences \
collapse to the same\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"35c9639f-7d05-4bf8-b429-c42b2021fb39"],

Cell["reduced Main-visible readout whenever: ", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"fe1db6a0-eca2-4742-871f-c13a3891d405"],

Cell["the accepted-record reduction agrees,", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"2e7a9545-641a-411d-aa8a-d60564002e98"],

Cell["the common reduced welded projection is used,", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"96b73ace-b2b1-498b-b877-2e99a7a695e2"],

Cell["\<\
and no explicit accepted-record failure or explicit leakage branch is \
introduced.\
\>", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"5bc5d8cb-ac12-466c-8cae-f7a30234f20e"],

Cell["\<\
Any remaining unreduced seam/source/tangent differences are theorem-invisible \
to the Main-visible\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"2e4c3a3a-7ef5-4a31-826f-1e8ea60794bf"],

Cell["\<\
quotient as formulated here. That is fully consistent with the source note's \
corrected distinction\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"c44d9051-24d2-4137-935c-a5ab83bc06e8"],

Cell["\<\
between theorem-visible reduced data and stronger unreduced source/tangent \
factorization targets. \
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"1c05694c-d311-48c2-aa92-4964bbc27eb2"],

Cell["Top-Line Verdict", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"4acc54c6-3540-4b5e-b764-f40321f49a45"],

Cell[TextData[{
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["\<\
Main-visible quotient survives exact receiver-closure audit in the current \
family\
\>",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"48889607-3fa3-4d45-b059-5e8f16cbf2e7"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"ced91171-5e77-457c-91a5-77371dfdccc6"],
 "with the sharper exact reading: ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["\<\
No reduced exact falsifier was found; the quotient fibers are rank-one/scalar \
in the current audited family, not richer.\
\>",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"2a9d164a-dd67-4673-a14e-eeb754194fd8"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"13d36443-b6aa-46b9-a6ef-888edd65632d"]
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"2feb13e2-9908-4fc2-8038-280570d04414"],

Cell["Non-Claims", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"26f9b26e-d72f-4496-aa37-70ab7d74f218"],

Cell["This is not source-internal theorem promotion.", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"b716ef0a-166b-41f2-9fc1-40791706f1fc"],

Cell["\<\
This does not prove full unreduced seam/source/tangent agreement.\
\>", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"0aa74798-2d2d-4108-b142-8b6830f7c19d"],

Cell["\<\
This does not enlarge Main beyond the abstract weak-interface data it already \
consumes.\
\>", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"63866ac3-98ef-4000-bd76-1b89c4e20e39"],

Cell["\<\
This does not discharge leakage or accepted-record failure cases; those \
remain explicit exceptions.\
\>", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"b8c04929-c818-4f61-b8fd-da0c88f0c342"]
},
FrontEndVersion->"14.3 for Linux x86 (64-bit) (July 8, 2025)",
